snippet.title: Moroi: Welcome to The Cosmic Engine
snippet.description:
Behold... The Cosmic Engine.

Part prison, part purgatory, these twisting halls of torment are the only reality you've ever known. Follow its rules, meet its inhabitants, play its games. Maybe, just maybe, you can make it out with your sanity in tact.

Moroi is coming soon to PC. Play the demo on Steam today:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2518410/Moroi/

Developed by Violet Saint, Published by Good Shepherd Entertainment.
https://www.goodshepherd.games/games/moroi
